            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>Fixed</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Microphone access in notarized builds.</strong> Dictation could not access the microphone in Developer&nbsp;ID / notarized builds even when Microphone was granted in System Settings. The hardened runtime requires the audio-input entitlement, which was missing — now added.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
